

05/04/2021 - Waterfall, Agile, Scrum

the interview questions
1. What is Agile
2. what are the values of Agile(Agile Manifesto) 
    People over process and tools
    Working software over comprehensive documentation
    Customer collaboration over rigid contracts
    Responding to change rather than following a plan
3.what is Scrum
 	Scrum is providing the highest value in the shortest time

 	SME- Subject Matter Expert

 	Definition of Ready - when the user story is ready with all the acceptance criteria

 	Definition of done - when the user story is completed.









